## Test Suite 6: Undo System & Polish (Phase 3.5)

### Test 6.1: Undo Single Delete

**Steps:**
1. Delete a time entry
2. Verify undo toast appears
3. Click "Undo" button within 10 seconds

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Toast shows "Time entry deleted"
- ✅ "Undo" button visible
- ✅ Clicking undo restores entry
- ✅ Entry reappears in list with all data intact
- ✅ Toast dismisses after undo

---

### Test 6.2: Undo Auto-Expire

**Steps:**
1. Delete a time entry
2. Wait 10+ seconds without clicking undo
3. Verify toast disappears

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Toast auto-dismisses at 10 seconds
- ✅ Entry remains deleted
- ✅ No errors in console

---

### Test 6.3: Undo Bulk Delete

**Steps:**
1. Select 7 time entries
2. Bulk delete them
3. Click "Undo" within 10 seconds

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Toast shows "7 entries deleted"
- ✅ All 7 entries restore correctly
- ✅ Order preserved
- ✅ All metadata intact (projects, notes, etc.)

---

### Test 6.4: Multiple Undo Actions

**Steps:**
1. Delete entry A
2. Delete entry B (before first toast expires)
3. Delete entry C
4. Undo entry B
5. Undo entry C
6. Let entry A expire

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Multiple toasts stack vertically
- ✅ Each undo acts on correct entry
- ✅ Expired actions cannot be undone
- ✅ No state corruption

---

### Test 6.5: Edit Modal - Project & Notes

**Steps:**
1. Click "Edit" on a time entry
2. Change project to different project
3. Add/modify notes
4. Save changes

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Project selector shows current project
- ✅ Can change to any project or "No Project"
- ✅ Notes textarea preserves line breaks
- ✅ Changes save correctly
- ✅ Entry list updates immediately

