## Cross-Feature Integration Tests

### Integration Test 1: Full Workflow

**Steps:**
1. Create project "Client Work"
2. Create manual entry with project, notes
3. View entry in calendar
4. Export to CSV, verify entry present
5. Edit entry to change project
6. Bulk delete entry
7. Undo deletion
8. View monthly report, verify entry counted

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ All features work together seamlessly
- ✅ Data consistency across all views
- ✅ No errors or warnings

---

### Integration Test 2: Dark Mode Consistency

**Steps:**
1. Toggle to dark mode
2. Test each feature:
   - Create project (check color visibility)
   - Manual entry modal (check form readability)
   - Monthly report (check heat map contrast)
   - Calendar view (check entry blocks)
   - Undo toast (check button contrast)

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ All text readable (WCAG AA contrast)
- ✅ Project colors visible on dark backgrounds
- ✅ No white/light flashes
- ✅ Interactive elements clearly visible

---

## Performance Tests

### Performance Test 1: Large Dataset

**Steps:**
1. Create 50+ time entries spanning multiple months
2. Navigate between views (Entries, Calendar, Reports)
3. Apply filters
4. Export CSV

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ No lag or freezing
- ✅ Pagination handles large lists
- ✅ Calendar renders smoothly
- ✅ Export completes in <5 seconds

---

### Performance Test 2: Rapid Interactions

**Steps:**
1. Quickly toggle between months in calendar
2. Rapidly select/deselect entries
3. Spam bulk operations (with undo)

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ UI remains responsive
- ✅ No race conditions
- ✅ No duplicate toasts or actions
- ✅ State updates correctly

---

## Edge Cases & Error Handling

### Edge Case 1: Empty States

**Steps:**
1. Delete all time entries
2. Delete all projects
3. View each tab: Timer, Entries, Calendar, Reports

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ "No entries" messages display
- ✅ "No projects" messages display
- ✅ No JavaScript errors
- ✅ UI prompts user to create first entry/project

---

### Edge Case 2: Long Text

**Steps:**
1. Create entry with 500-character description
2. Create project with 100-character name
3. Add 1000-character notes

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Text truncates gracefully in lists
- ✅ Full text visible in edit modals
- ✅ CSV export includes full text
- ✅ No layout breaking

---

### Edge Case 3: Special Characters

**Steps:**
1. Create entry with description: `Test "quotes", commas, and 日本語`
2. Export to CSV
3. Open CSV and verify

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Special characters preserved
- ✅ Quotes properly escaped in CSV
- ✅ Unicode characters (emoji, CJK) display correctly

---

### Edge Case 4: Time Zones

**Steps:**
1. Create entry at 23:30 (near midnight)
2. Create entry spanning midnight (23:30 - 00:30)
3. View in calendar and reports

**Expected Results:**
- ✅ Times stored in local timezone
- ✅ Dates display correctly
- ✅ Midnight-spanning entries show on correct days
- ✅ Duration calculations accurate

---

