## Final Verification Checklist

### Code Quality
- ✅ TypeScript compilation passes (`npm run type-check`)
- ✅ No console errors during testing
- ✅ No console warnings (or documented exceptions)
- ✅ Build succeeds (`npm run build`)
- ✅ Bundle size <100KB gzipped

### Accessibility (WCAG AA)
- ✅ All interactive elements keyboard accessible
- ✅ Focus indicators visible
- ✅ Color contrast ratios compliant
- ✅ Screen reader labels present (aria-label)

### Security
- ✅ No XSS vulnerabilities (user input sanitized)
- ✅ No SQL injection (using IndexedDB parameterized queries)
- ✅ No sensitive data in localStorage/console

### Privacy
- ✅ All data stored locally (IndexedDB)
- ✅ No network requests to external servers
- ✅ Export data contains only user data

